summary: Re-textured Tera armor to look similar to vanilla armor. Requires asianboy345\'s original mod.
descriptionHtml:
This mod aims to re-texture several of the armors from asianboy345\'s Tera armor mod with textures similar to those of vanilla armors.

Requirements:

>UNP
http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/6709

>asianboy345\'s Tera UNP armor mod
http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/25846


-Credits-
Bethesda
En Masse Entertainment
asianboy345
author: corsairsx
